      • Disease

        public Disease(int contagiousRange,
               int contagiousPercent,
               int baseMortalityRate,
               int baseMinTimeSick,
               int baseMaxTimeSick,
               int startPercentHealthy)
        Creates a disease object to be handed to each person
        Parameters:
        contagiousRange - The number of pixels two people must be within for a healthy person to become sick for an infected person
        contagiousPercent - The percent chance each tick that a sick person will infect a healthy person when within range
        baseMortalityRate - The base mortality rate for the disease (Changes depending on a person's age and pre-existing conditions
        baseMinTimeSick - The minimum time sick a person can be sick for (affected by the age of the person)
        baseMaxTimeSick - The maximum time sick a person can be sick for
        startPercentHealthy - The percent of people that start off as healthy in the simulation
